  "title": "Assistant Architectural Manager",
  "description": "<p>Our esteemed client in the <strong>Construction industry</strong> is seeking an <strong>Assistant Architectural Manager </strong>to join their dynamic team:</p><ul><li><strong>Employment Type: </strong>Permanent</li><li><strong>Position:</strong> Assistant<strong> </strong>Architectural Manager</li><li><strong>Location:</strong> Central</li><li><strong>Working Hours:</strong> 5 days, Office Hours</li><li><strong>Salary Package:</strong> Basic + Bonus</li></ul><p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Lead and guide a team of design coordinators and architects in managing architectural aspects of projects, ensuring adherence to specifications, timelines, and quality standards.</li><li>Oversee the planning, organization, and supervision of construction drawing production, including shop drawing submissions for approval.</li><li>Act as the primary architectural liaison between consultants, clients, and subcontractors to ensure accurate interpretation and implementation of design drawings and details.</li><li>Ensure full compliance with all regulatory standards, codes of practice, and company protocols.</li><li>Provide technical support to the site team, resolving design discrepancies and coordination issues with structural, M&E, and interior works.</li><li>Conduct regular site inspections to verify workmanship and materials meet design requirements.</li><li>Assist senior management in preparing reports, managing documentation, and representing the team in coordination meetings.</li></ul><p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Minimum 8 years of relevant experience with a main contractor firm.</li><li>At least Degree in Architecture.</li><li>Familiar with local submission and authority processes.</li></ul><p><br /></p><p><strong>Ready to apply? Here’s how:</strong></p><ul><li>Click the APPLY button, or</li><li>Email your resume (in MS Word or PDF format) to <a href=\"mailto:adelin@intuitrecruitment.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>adelin@intuitrecruitment.com</strong>.</a> Include the job title in your email subject line for prompt processing.</li></ul><p><em><strong>Only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</strong></em></p><p><br /></p><p>By submitting your application, you consent to the collection and use of your personal data under Personal Data Protection Act (PDPA).</p><p><br /></p><p>Adelin Chong | EA Personnel Reg No.: R1875641</p><p>Intuit Recruitment Pte Ltd | EA License No.: 25C2793</p>",
